# GraphQL
GET         /graphql              controllers.graphql.GraphQlController.graphql(query: String, variables: Option[String], operation: Option[String])
POST        /graphql              controllers.graphql.GraphQlController.graphqlBody
GET         /render-schema        controllers.graphql.GraphQlController.renderSchema
